N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 115.1 - Reports of caseload activity information

State Regulations

The Chief Administrator of the Courts may
prescribe forms and systems for the reporting of caseload activity information
for each court of the Unified Court System. Notes
